Well, I made it from surgery!! Yay!!! LOL Well there was no chance I 
wasn't gonna make it out.. but when they put the injections in, Mum 
sure thought so.. *wince, but laughs at her Mum* I thought she was 
more scared about it than I was. 7 injections in the right ear and 
about 5 in the other.. *sigh*

But the numbing stuff (anisthetic.. spelling mistake, I'm sure of it) 
is still working, so I'm in a good mood. Apart from the fact that my 
bandage looks like an onion wrapped around my head.. without the 
pointy bit at the top *_* And it'll be there for the next week. WAH!!

Thanks to Zardus, Carnage, Soulstice and Airshadow for wishing me 
well *_*

Okay.. so.. talk to ya later!
